   <narrative xml:lang="EN">No Isolation for kids at hospital</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program has 2 main objectives :   1/ reduce young patients&apos; relational isolation and loneliness  and maintain close contact with their relatives/school/friends during long-term hospitalizations ; 2/ Facilitate the return to school and to the family, limit the psychological impacts on siblings. This is possible thanks to an easy-to-use robot being the avatar of the patient outside. The robot has become unavoidable in this period of pandemic and dramatically increased patient isolation.</narrative>
  </description>
